---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero__inner">

    <div class="hero__content">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">Trusted by Students Worldwide</p>
      <h1>Expert Academic Writing & Research Support</h1>
      <p class="hero__sub">From high school essays to PhD dissertations — we provide expert guidance, writing support, and professional editing at every academic level.</p>

      <div class="hero__buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Get a Free Quote</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__trust">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">2,000+</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Students Helped</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">98%</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Satisfaction Rate</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">50+</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Expert Writers</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__visual">
      <div class="hero__card">
        <div class="card__icon">✦</div>
        <h3>Your Academic Journey Starts Here</h3>
        <p>From first assignment to final defence — we support you every step of the way.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>✓ Essays & Assignment Help</li>
          <li>✓ Research Papers & Reports</li>
          <li>✓ Dissertation & Thesis Support</li>
          <li>✓ Editing & Proofreading</li>
          <li>✓ Academic Integrity Guaranteed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  background-color: var(--navy);
  padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -50%;
  right: -20%;
  width: 600px;
  height: 600px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(197,160,89,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.hero__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.hero__eyebrow {
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.hero h1 {
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.hero__sub {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 520px;
}

.hero__buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.hero__trust {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.trust-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.2rem;
}

.trust-number {
  color: var(--gold);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1;
}

.trust-label {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.trust-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 40px;
  background-color: var(--border);
}

.hero__visual {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

.hero__card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 380px;
  width: 100%;
}

.card__icon {
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.hero__card h3 {
  color: var(--white);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.hero__card > p {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.hero__card ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.7rem;
}

.hero__card ul li {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
  }
  .hero__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .hero__visual {
    display: none;
  }
  .hero__trust {
    gap: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>